 <svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"w-5 h-5 ml-2\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path stroke=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0z\" fill=\"none\"></path><path d=\"M17 7l-10 10\"></path><path d=\"M8 7l9 0l0 9\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"bg-zinc-50\"><div class=\"container py-8 text-center lg:py-0 lg:text-left lg:flex lg:justify-between \"><div class=\"lg:w-1/2 xl:py-14 lg:py-8\"><p class=\"tracking-widest\">OFFER FOR THE BEST INTERIOR</p><h1 class=\"py-4 text-3xl font-extrabold leading-tight text-gray-800 xl:text-6xl lg:text-4xl\">An aesthetic room is <br/>given harmony</h1><p class=\"pb-6 text-gray-500 xl:pb-10\">Change your view with the best interior design. <br/> We provide the best interior design for your Home. <br/>Make every moment beautiful with the best interior design.</p></div><div class=\"w-1/2\"><img alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"absolute right-0 xl:h-[448px] xl:w-[700px] lg:h-[344px] lg:w-[500px]  hidden lg:block\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimage%2Fkitchen.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimage%2Fkitchen.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimage%2Fkitchen.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/></div></div></div><div class=\"py-4 bg-zinc-100\"></div><div class=\"container py-16\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between pb-4\"><a class=\"py-4 text-3xl font-extrabold leading-tight text-gray-800 lg:text-5xl\" href=\"\">An aesthetic room is <br/>given harmony</a></div><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 place-items-center \"><div><img alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"500\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"max-md:hidden\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimage%2Fs4.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimage%2Fs4.jpg&amp;w=1920&a